### Summary of Appendix 3H - Notification of Cessation of Securities  

- **Cessation of Unquoted Options**:  
  - **AVHAAN**: 5,050 lapsed (expiry 01-Jul-2032 @ USD 4.97) – ceased 28-Jun-2025.  
  - **AVHABI**: 3,000 lapsed (expiry 04-Jan-2034 @ USD 12.64) – ceased 18-Jul-2025 & 19-Jul-2025.  
  - **AVHAAP**: 5,000 lapsed (expiry 05-Oct-2032 @ USD 5.16) – ceased 18-Jul-2025 & 19-Jul-2025.  
  - **AVHABP**: 8,000 lapsed (expiry 22-Jan-2035 @ USD 8.73) – ceased 28-Jun-2025.  
  - **AVHAAV**: 1,333 lapsed (expiry 07-Jun-2033 @ USD 14.17) – ceased 28-Jun-2025.  
  - **AVHABB**: 5,333 expired unexercised (expiry 04-Jan-2034 @ USD 12.64) – ceased 28-Jun-2025.  

- **Reason**: All cessations due to lapse/expiry of conditional rights or options.  
- **Impact**: No material change to capital structure or liquidity (insignificant volumes relative to total issued capital).  

**No material trading or valuation impact identified.**  

*(Note: Other unquoted options remain outstanding per Part 3, but no new material disclosures.)*
